flowRoot.flowPara: We are an ambitious, aggressive movement with far-reaching goals.
Our organization's name is "Earth Strike" - two words, with a space (no hyphen) between them. ALL-CAPS is recommended.

Our primary tagline is "General Strike to Save the Planet". When not displayed in all caps, all words except "to" and "the" should start with a capital letter. The words "to" and "Save" should not have a line break between them.
General strike to save the planet
General Strike to Save the Planet
General Strike To Save The Planet
unnecessary sexually, racially, or politically-charged language
condemnations of the rich and powerful
accurately-worded facts and statistics, backed up with sources
We are something new. Our general strike is our selling point that distinguishes us from other climate movements.
We are not stuck in the past. We are mindful of current events and trends.
We should not distract from our central message. Our content must be easy to digest and accessible to everyone.
